---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: "help_output(& [\"tools\", \"--help\"])"
---
Manage hpds-installed formatter/linter tools (advanced)

Usage: hpds tools [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list    List installed tools and their versions
  update  Refresh tools to release defaults or config pins
  clean   Remove the tool cache
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -v, --verbose        Show more detail (underlying commands, tool names)
  -q, --quiet          Suppress all output except errors
      --no-color       Disable colored output
      --config <PATH>  Use this config file instead of discovering hpds.toml
  -h, --help           Print help
